text: Esther Sanz (born 6 December 1974) is a Spanish badminton player, born in Málaga. She competed in women's singles at the 1992 Summer Olympics in Barcelona. ==References== ==External links== * Category:1974 births Category:Living people Category:Spanish female badminton players Category:Olympic badminton players of Spain Category:Badminton players at the 1992 Summer Olympics Category:Sportspeople from Málaga
